        </p>
        <p>
          In the <url href="https://www.rossmanchance.com/applets/2021/power/Power.html" visual="rossmanchance.com/applets/2021/power/Power.html">Power Simulation applet</url>:
        </p>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li><p>Specify the Hypothesized probability of success: 0.25</p></li>
