            <li><p>Press <c>Draw Samples</c></p></li>
            <li><p>Choose <c>Proportion of successes</c> as the statistic</p></li>
            <li><p>Use the pull-down menu to set the Level of Significance to 0.05</p></li>
            <li><p>Press <c>Count</c></p></li>
            <li><p>Check the <c>Normal Approximation</c> and <c>Summary Stats</c> boxes to verify <xref ref="I1-11-b" text="local">Checkpoint</xref></p></li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
          Report the rejection region found by the applet and include a one-sentence interpretation of this region.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rejection region: <var width="20"/>
        </p>
